Usage: setPGPinUseSignalRoute [-help] [<cellPins>] [-all] [-off] [-well]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<cellPins>                          # cell:pin pair (list, optional)
-all                                # route all backup and non-main_rail
                                    # primary power/ground pins (bool, optional)
-off                                # reset (bool, optional)
-well                               # include nwell and pwell pins
                                    # (bool, optional)